Browse Channels Man Tries to Clean Gutters on Precarious Ladder, the Inevitable Happens 
Doug Miller wanted to clean his gutters out at his home in Liverpool, New York, but there was one problem – his ladder wouldn’t reach the roof.Doug decided to improvise by placing the ladder on two tables to increase his reach. However, it didn’t go according to plan for poor Doug. Ouch! Credit: Doug Miller via Storyful
